trans-unit.source: Implements a markup extension that supports dynamic resource references made from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Implementerer filtypen markup som støtter dynamiske ressursen referanser fra [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Dynamic resource references are necessary when referencing content that might change at run-time.
trans-unit.target: Refererer til dynamiske ressursen er nødvendig når refererer til innhold som kan endres under kjøring.

trans-unit.source: The reasons for the content change might be application-initiated or might be external.
trans-unit.target: Grunner til innhold endringen kanskje programmet startet eller kan være ekstern.

trans-unit.source: One example is if you are including styles that rely on system resources that report user-configured preferences, such as themes, font settings and so on.
trans-unit.target: Et eksempel er Hvis du inkluderer stiler som avhenger av systemressurser som rapporterer Brukerkonfigurert innstillinger, for eksempel tema, skriftinnstillinger og så videre.

trans-unit.source: This class is a markup extension implementation.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen er en markup utvidelsen implementering.

trans-unit.source: Markup extension classes in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] exist mainly to provide infrastructure support for some aspect of the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] processor implementation, and the members exposed by the markup extension classes are not typically called from directly user code.
trans-unit.target: Markup utvidelsen klasser i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] finnes først og fremst for å gi infrastruktur støtte for deler av det [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] prosessor implementering og medlemmer vises av markup utvidelsen klassene ikke kalles fra direkte brukerkode.

trans-unit.source: This class particularly supports the [DynamicResource Markup Extension](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) usage from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen spesielt støtter den [DynamicResource Markup utvidelsen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) Bruk fra [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: For more information about dynamic resource references, see [DynamicResource Markup Extension](../Topic/DynamicResource%20Markup%20Extension.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om dynamiske ressursen referanser [DynamicResource Markup filtypen](../Topic/DynamicResource%20Markup%20Extension.md).

trans-unit.source: ## XAML Text Usage For [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] information, see [DynamicResource Markup Extension](../Topic/DynamicResource%20Markup%20Extension.md).
trans-unit.target: ## XAML tekst-Bruk For [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] informasjon, se [DynamicResource Markup filtypen](../Topic/DynamicResource%20Markup%20Extension.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.DynamicResourceExtension"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.DynamicResourceExtension"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.DynamicResourceExtension"></xref> class, with the provided initial key.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.DynamicResourceExtension"> </xref> klasse, med den angitte opprinnelige nøkkelen.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is used by [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] processors when processing the attribute syntax for the [DynamicResource Markup Extension](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren brukes av [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] prosessorer under behandling av Attributtsyntaksen for den [DynamicResource Markup filtypen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The key of the resource that this markup extension references.
trans-unit.target: Nøkkelen for ressursen som refererer til denne markup utvidelsen.

trans-unit.source: Returns an object that should be set on the property where this extension is applied.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et objekt som skal angis for egenskapen der denne utvidelsen skal brukes.

trans-unit.source: For <xref href="System.Windows.DynamicResourceExtension"></xref>, this is the object found in a resource dictionary in the current parent chain that is keyed by the <xref:System.Windows.DynamicResourceExtension.ResourceKey*>.
trans-unit.target: For <xref href="System.Windows.DynamicResourceExtension"> </xref>, dette er objekt funnet i en ordliste for ressursen i gjeldende overordnet kjeden som har av <xref:System.Windows.DynamicResourceExtension.ResourceKey*>.</xref:System.Windows.DynamicResourceExtension.ResourceKey*>

trans-unit.source: This method supports [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] processor implementation, and is not intended to be called directly.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden støtter [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] prosessor implementering og skal ikke kalles direkte.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] processor implementation uses this method for proper handling of [DynamicResource Markup Extension](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) values during object creation.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] prosessor implementering bruker denne metoden for riktig behandling av [DynamicResource Markup utvidelsen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) verdier under opprettelse av objekt.

trans-unit.source: The property to be set by the provided value must be of type <xref:System.Windows.DependencyProperty>.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angis av den angitte verdien må være av typen <xref:System.Windows.DependencyProperty>.</xref:System.Windows.DependencyProperty>

trans-unit.source: This implementation does not rely on any services based on the passed `serviceProvider`.
trans-unit.target: Denne implementeringen ikke avhenger av tjenester basert på den innsendte `serviceProvider`.

trans-unit.source: Object that can provide services for the markup extension.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som kan gi tjenester for markup filtypen.

trans-unit.source: The object to set on the property where the extension is applied.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som angitt i egenskapen der utvidelsen skal brukes.

trans-unit.source: Rather than the actual value, this will be an expression that will be evaluated at a later time.
trans-unit.target: Dette vil være et uttrykk som evalueres senere i stedet for den faktiske verdien.

trans-unit.source: Attempted to provide a value for an extension that did not provide a resourceKey.
trans-unit.target: Forsøk på å angi en verdi for en filtype som ikke oppgav et resourceKey .

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the key specified by this dynamic resource reference.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir nøkkelen som er angitt av denne dynamiske ressursreferanse.

trans-unit.source: The key is used to lookup a resource in resource dictionaries, by means of an intermediate expression.
trans-unit.target: Nøkkelen brukes til å slå opp en ressurs i ressursen ordlister ved hjelp av et mellomliggende uttrykk.

trans-unit.source: The key is not strongly typed, but is usually provided as either a string, a <xref:System.Type>, or a <xref:System.Windows.ResourceKey> derived class.
trans-unit.target: Nøkkelen er ikke sterkt skrevet, men vanligvis er angitt som enten en streng, en <xref:System.Type>, eller en <xref:System.Windows.ResourceKey>avledet klasse.</xref:System.Windows.ResourceKey> </xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.target: ## XAML tekst-Bruk For [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] informasjon, se [DynamicResource Markup filtypen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The resource key that this dynamic resource reference specifies.
trans-unit.target: Ressursnøkkelen som angir denne dynamiske ressursreferanse.
